| CCSDS    | Consultative Committee for Space Data Systems - international standards body |
| COG      | Cloud Optimized GeoTIFF - efficient cloud-native imagery format              |
| EPS      | Electrical Power System                                                      |
| GEOINT   | Geospatial Intelligence                                                      |
| SAR      | Synthetic Aperture Radar                                                     |
| STAC     | SpatioTemporal Asset Catalog - specification for geospatial data discovery   |
| TLE      | Two-Line Element - orbital parameter format for satellite tracking           |
| TT&C     | Tracking, Telemetry, and Command                                             |

